", "id": "714271887405360", "uri": "https://scontent-lga3-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982547_714271890738693_265093282870496168_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=OXCo8GGheuYQ7kNvgFFyR6-&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB-GvI8PMTqOcONU1bu52Y4Wnxly3VJMm7KGGaZLWwYSA&oe=67602149"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "\u5c01\u9762\u666f\u89c2-16-9-2560x1440\u50cf\u7d20-32\u4f4dPNG.png", "id": "3796693557286442", "uri": "https://scontent-lga3-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982688_3796693560619775_1594849867367252292_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=nq89dNXkF9YQ7kNvgFm76PH&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDpzDsM0p8y9UN9gGSl83AvWpLJhWpEjLE6WRD9FN40Zw&oe=67601D56"}, "display_name": "Lightning Archer", "keywords": ["Lightning", "Archer", "Archery", "TD"], "long_description": "**\"Lightning Archer\"** takes you to Elyria, a planet on the edge of collapse due to war and destruction. As the chief archer, defend your cities in **24** mission levels and 3 arenas against **31** unique enemies, from warriors to mages.  Wield your enchanted bow and fight to save Elyria!!\n{496528779662703}\n# Game Highlights:\n# 360\u00b0 Immersive Tower Defense Game.\nImmerse yourself in a revolutionary tower defense game that amplifies direct combat with monsters from every angle. Engage in thrilling 360-degree battles, offering a more dynamic and realistic combat experience.\n#  Diverse and Challenging Monsters and Bosses\nFace off against **31** unique monsters, including warriors, mages, and flying creatures, each with distinct attack styles and defenses. Every encounter presents a new challenge, making every shot count and keeping gameplay exciting.\n# Rich Level Content\nExplore **24** mission levels and **3** arenas across diverse environments like forests, deserts, and islands. Discover hidden gameplay elements that offer endless replayability and keep you coming back for more.\n{407707755143988}\n# Stunning Magical Skills\nUnleash **5** powerful Magic skills and **11** Rune skills. Beyond regular attacks, summon divine beasts with rune skills to aid you in taking down formidable Bosses.\n{865256208361627}\n# Earn Your Battle Honor\nUnlock **18** medals and **6** secret easter egg medals and compete for glory on the global leaderboard. Prove your skills and claim your place among the elite.\n\n", "short_description": "\"Lightning Archer\" takes you to Elyria, a planet on the edge of collapse due to war and destruction. As the chief archer, defend your cities in 24 mission levels and 3 arenas against 31 unique enemies, from warriors to mages. Wield your enchanted bow and fight to save Elyria!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "2560x1440\u50cf\u7d20-\u6587\u5b57\u4e0b\u9762\u7528\u56fe002_Spanish.png", "id": "4063052394020821", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent-lga3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031403_4063052397354154_8305071370850845551_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=EUm9cl0pPkAQ7kNvgEzvgw5&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAkDwAlFZSQhizYUbGm3AbgxzjVjpYDFe7_-9ryys3xUA&oe=676025F6"}, {"file_name": "2560x1440\u50cf\u7d20-\u6587\u5b57\u4e0b\u9762\u7528\u56fe001-Spanish.png", "id": "1485137028802785", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent-lga3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982629_1485137032136118_3844618734780280379_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=pYAfVru8kXYQ7kNvgETr2Mz&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAoSgz0HVZAyhgtMOj7FNJgtxjStR4YEuGT1V0S_Ae0XA&oe=67601015"}, {"file_name": "2560x1440\u50cf\u7d20-\u6587\u5b57\u4e0b\u9762\u7528\u56fe003_Spanish.png", "id": "848764617211802", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent-lga3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001675_848764623878468_3695105967758461101_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Y3ytyTk8xr0Q7kNvgEKQnWt&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBYK30X5Vh5Dzlm2NE05BZRRIOGdVVilOVXS6uO4imiqw&oe=676016FB"}, {"file_name": "2560x1440\u50cf\u7d20-\u6587\u5b57\u4e0b\u9762\u7528\u56fe003_Spanish.png", "id": "534293912367786", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent-lga3-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75250457_534293915701119_1438204843830935264_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vE4Sgtu8OboQ7kNvgG8IV4P&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCKcGD9-2My6ZPAa5u71Ei2nRXGuJ_ehGNpi1yVsGPoqg&oe=676021CC"}]}, "id": "2319124261772577", "locale": "es_LA", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "\u5c01\u9762\u666f\u89c2-16-9-2560x1440\u50cf\u7d20-32\u4f4dPNG.png", "id": "538032658654052", "uri": "https://scontent-lga3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003272_538032665320718_4473136547506745553_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3tLod075tIIQ7kNvgHo_LFA&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAnpQhkfOl9FV_ygSAtb4FYnawskIk3LfmhxqRO0q0XcQ&oe=67602723"}, "display_name": "Arquero Rel\u00e1mpago", "keywords": ["Arquero", "Lightning", "Archer", "TD"], "long_description": "**\"Arquero Rel\u00e1mpago\"** te lleva a Elyria, un planeta al borde del colapso debido a la guerra y la destrucci\u00f3n. Como el arquero jefe, defiende tus ciudades en **24** niveles de misi\u00f3n y **3** arenas contra **31** enemigos \u00fanicos, desde guerreros hasta magos. \n\n{534293912367786}\n# Puntos Destacados del Juego:\n# Juego de Defensa de Torres Inmersivo a 360\u00b0\nSum\u00e9rgete en un juego de defensa de torres revolucionario que amplifica el combate directo con monstruos desde todos los \u00e1ngulos. Enfr\u00e9ntate a emocionantes batallas de 360 grados, ofreciendo una experiencia de combate m\u00e1s din\u00e1mica y realista.\n\n# Monstruos y Jefes Diversos y Desafiantes\nEnfr\u00e9ntate a **31** monstruos \u00fanicos, incluidos guerreros, magos y criaturas voladoras, cada uno con estilos de ataque y defensas distintivos. Cada encuentro presenta un nuevo desaf\u00edo, haciendo que cada disparo cuente y manteniendo el juego emocionante.\n\n# Contenido de Niveles Rico\nExplora **24** niveles de misi\u00f3n y **3** arenas a trav\u00e9s de diversos entornos como bosques, desiertos e islas. Descubre elementos de juego ocultos que ofrecen una rejugabilidad infinita y te mantienen regresando por m\u00e1s.{1485137028802785}\n# Habilidades M\u00e1gicas Impresionantes\nDesata **5** poderosas habilidades m\u00e1gicas y **11** habilidades r\u00fanicas. M\u00e1s all\u00e1 de los ataques regulares, invoca bestias divinas con habilidades r\u00fanicas para ayudarte a derrotar a jefes formidables.\n{4063052394020821}\n# Gana Tu Honor en la Batalla\nDesbloquea **18** medallas y **6** medallas secretas de huevos de pascua, y compite por la gloria en la tabla de clasificaci\u00f3n global. \n", "short_description": "\"Arquero Rel\u00e1mpago\" te lleva a Elyria, un planeta al borde del colapso debido a la guerra y la destrucci\u00f3n. Como el arquero jefe, defiende tus ciudades en 24 niveles de misi\u00f3n y 3 arenas contra 31 enemigos \u00fanicos, desde guerreros hasta magos. \u00a1Empu\u00f1a tu arco encantado y lucha para salvar Elyria!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "2560x1440\u50cf\u7d20-\u6587\u5b57\u4e0b\u9762\u7528\u56fe003_Japanese.png", "id": "7840431482752448", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent-lga3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974655_7840431486085781_6257258386486932911_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1S24TNBgGXgQ7kNvgFT6whD&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDNMJ8Aniuo3t6rIPHZp58u6yHyygkZRO7un8YuomLnTQ&oe=67602A20"}, {"file_name": "2560x1440\u50cf\u7d20-\u6587\u5b57\u4e0b\u9762\u7528\u56fe001-Japanese.png", "id": "1175596193561322", "image_type": "APP_IMG_MARKDOWN_INLINE", "uri": "https://scontent-lga3-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75230038_1175596196894655_2303592424450330524_n