ts.", "created_date": 1725962538, "id": "8774173962601773", "version": "2.3", "version_code": 14, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7083616814990838", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8774173962601773"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1066836174691117"}]}, "change_log": "Now we add French, Japanese and Spanish support.", "created_date": 1723794607, "id": "8617809328238238", "version": "2.2", "version_code": 12, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7083616814990838", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8774173962601773"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1066836174691117"}]}, "change_log": "Version 2.1\n1. Added 12 new monsters with unique gameplay mechanics.\n2. Added 16 new mission levels, offering more fun and challenges.\n3. Each battle mode now records the highest score, with leaderboards ranked by the total of the highest scores from three arenas.\n4. Other usability and stability improvements.", "created_date": 1723103054, "id": "8568727223146449", "version": "2.1", "version_code": 11, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7083616814990838", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8774173962601773"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1066836174691117"}]}, "change_log": "Release Notes V2.0\n\t1. New Level Mode: Introduced level mode with shorter durations and more diverse gameplay options.\n\t2. Monster Attacks: Monsters can now attack players, requiring timely shield defense.\n\t3. New Magic Arrow: Introduced the tracking arrow, which can lock onto and follow monsters.\n\t4. New Monsters: Added two new types of monsters \u2013 archers and flying dragons.\n\t5. Elite Monsters: High-level monsters now have health points and can be defeated with headshots.\n\t6. Enhanced Visuals: Improved incentive effects and better interface display.\n\t7. Usability and Stability: Various other usability and stability improvements.", "created_date": 1721371493, "id": "8447641658588340", "version": "2.0", "version_code": 10, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7083616814990838", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8774173962601773"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1066836174691117"}]}, "change_log": "\u201cV1.2.0\n1. Added two new types of monster: Bomb Bird and Bomberman.\n2. Electric towers can attack any monsters except for Bosses, with activation count changed from time-based to attack count-based.\n3. Players can immediately respawn in the same place if they fail to defeat a Boss.\nV1.1.0\n1. Added a new training ground for beginners to help new users master the use of skills.\n2. Appropriately adjusted the difficulty levels of the stages.\u201d", "created_date": 1712741542, "id": "7953157761370068", "version": "1.2.0", "version_code": 8, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}